== Abbreviation ==
The abbreviation SAFT stands for [[Swiss Army Fitness Test]].

It also stands for 
Synthetic Aperture 
Focussing Technique(SAFT). The above method is used in image processing.

Also:
Statistical Associating Fluid Theory - An equation of state in thermodynamics, based on statistical mechanics, that takes into account molecular interactions.
